<ptxt>
DTC detecting condition
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Trouble area
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
B1513: Temperature Control Actuator and/or Its Circuit Malfunction
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Difference between target opening and actual opening is more than specified value even though temperature control actuator has operated for specified time.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Temperature control actuator circuit
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Temperature control actuator
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
HVAC control module
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
B1514: Air Flow Control Actuator and/or Its Circuit Malfunction
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Difference between target opening and actual opening is more than specified value even though air flow control actuator has operated for specified time.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Air flow control actuator circuit
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Air flow control actuator
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
HVAC control module
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</servinfosub>
