<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A7224020003">
<title>
DTC Confirmation Procedure
</title>
<topic id = "AENAP70A7224020004">
<title>
B1513
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Start engine and operate A/C system.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Change position of temperature selector from “LO” to “HI” gradually.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70A7224020005">
<title>
B1514
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Start engine and operate A/C system.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Push defroster switch to change position from “FACE” to “DEF”.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</topic>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A7224020006">
<title>
DTC Troubleshooting
</title>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
When DTC B1513 and/or B1514 is detected, check that there is any obstruction in opening range of actuator linkage.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
The following flow shows “DTC B1513: Temperature Control Actuator and/or Its Circuit Malfunction”.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Check “DTC B1514” in the same manner as “DTC B1513” referring to the following table.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "3" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "1.001in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "3.103in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "3.103in"/>
